    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, great-looking car without that 'fresh-off-the-lot' price tag. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. Come check it out, I'd love to show you around it!",
