    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS system. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate floor cracking, and the rod bearings were replaced at 90k miles. The suspension remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, and the cooling system has been refreshed with an aluminum radiator. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within factory spec. A true enthusiast's example optimized for turn-in precision and high-RPM performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Reliable vehicle in good condition. Maintenance is current. Clean interior and exterior. No known mechanical issues. Clear title.",
      "price": 29500.0,
