    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained SUV offers a perfect blend of luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery remains supple, and all high-tech features\u2014including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system\u2014are in perfect working order. Mechanically, this vehicle stands out with a comprehensive service history. It has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and we recently installed a new set of premium all-season tires and front brake rotors. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, confident ride. This is a reliable, well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34800.0,
