    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, well-loved, and totally ready for all your upcoming adventures. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty has plenty of life left in it. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
