    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for optimal timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback through refreshed control arm bushings and a set of balanced dampers. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all six cylinders remain within factory tolerances, ensuring peak performance for the next enthusiast.",
